high_descs: move to the counter to the left of the sink
pick up a mug from the coffee maker
move to the sink to the right of you
clean the mug in the sink
move to the counter to the left of the sink
put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned coffee mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk straight to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the coffee mug from the coffee maker.
Move to the right to face the sink.
Place the mug in the sink, fill the sink up with water and pick up the mug.
Move to the left to face the coffee machine.
Place the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place the mug filled with water in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right, proceed to counter with bread and knife on it across room.
Pick up coffee mug from coffee maker.
Move to the right to the sink.
Put mug in left side of sink, behind the fork.  Turn water on, then off, then drain water.  Pick up mug from sink.
Turn left, go back to coffee maker and face it.
Place mug back on coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Wash mug and return to coffee maker.
